(2, 'loan', 'loan', '贷款 (n.)', 'n.', '/ləʊn/', '{"meaning":"贷款 (n.)","examples":["We obtained a loan from the government. — 我们得了一笔政府贷款。","If you ask him for a loan, he''ll come through. — 如果你向他贷款，他会满足你的要求的。","The company won''t keep going unless we can get some loan. — 除非我们能搞到贷款，否则公司就维持不下去了。"],"etymology":null}', 494),
